title: Which songs from past albums will Taylor Swift sing during her Reputation tour? - Quora

response.answer_text: At the Santa Clara show, the referenced and performed songs from past albums were: Style / Love Story / You Belong with MeShake it OffWildest Dreams (acoustic)*Blank SpaceBad Blood / Should've Said NoLong LiveWe Are Never Getting Back TogetherWhile she sang Wildest Dreams in Santa Clara, she changed this song at other shows. At one show, she even sang Teardrops on My Guitar!
